{"calories":"890","carbs":93,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eWhether it’s date night or just a weekday dinner, we’re tempted by this deliciously decadent pasta. Mini pasta shells known as \u003cem\u003ecavatelli\u003c/em\u003e are tossed in a white wine–mushroom sauce made creamy with mascarpone cheese. An added burst of umami flavor comes from porcini mushroom powder, which is whisked into the pasta cooking water and used to thicken the dreamy sauce. Chives and a sprinkling of Parmesan cheese take this must-make meal to new heights.\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"0a698bbc4f","fat":46,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73530/large_cropped_sBDNFXYqQAq0m02ZrJGy_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_006_MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73533/iSOP1gUhTISdNGF9ROMq_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_005_HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73533/hero_iSOP1gUhTISdNGF9ROMq_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_005_HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73533/menu_small_iSOP1gUhTISdNGF9ROMq_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_005_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73533/small_square_iSOP1gUhTISdNGF9ROMq_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_005_HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73533/medium_square_iSOP1gUhTISdNGF9ROMq_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_005_HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73533/recipe_profile_page_iSOP1gUhTISdNGF9ROMq_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_005_HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73532/ENHzugyFQExpWtOmhNgj_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_010_MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73531/6HeLQZ94T06fhnKXNIJl_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_002_THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73531/menu_small_6HeLQZ94T06fhnKXNIJl_Mushroom_Cavatelli_with_Mascarpone_and_Chives_002_THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}}],"name":"Mushroom Cavatelli with Mascarpone and Chives","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":27,"public_slug":"mushroom-cavatelli-with-mascarpone-and-chives-9","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/55280/recipe_card20190719-10-1f0lgw6.pdf","recipe_id":7607,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Mushroom Cavatelli","subtitle":"with Mascarpone and Chives","title":"Mushroom Cavatelli","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWiping mushrooms clean instead of rinsing prevents them from absorbing water. They won't brown well if they're too wet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile it cooks, pasta releases starches into the boiling water. Using some reserved pasta water to make the porcini broth will help the sauce cling to the noodles. It’s easiest to reserve this water in a liquid measuring cup, if you have one.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["10\" large pot","12\" large high-sided pan"],"id":7607,"ingredients":["cremini mushrooms","chives","garlic","cavatelli pasta","unsalted butter","white wine","porcini mushroom powder","mascarpone cheese","grated Parmesan cheese"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"12.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"chives","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/242/medium_square_chives-2-test.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"cavatelli pasta","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2057/medium_square_cavatelli-pasta-2.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2371/medium_square_medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"porcini mushroom powder","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/548/medium_square_mushroom_powder.jpg"},{"name":"mascarpone cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1501/medium_square_MASCARPONE_CHEESE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2308/medium_square_PARM_copy.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73537/recipe_card_size_vz1glJ7sQ3OzgJ5k8kne_1__Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eBring a large pot of water to a boil over high heat. Wipe \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e clean with a damp paper towel and cut into .25-inch slices (see recipe tip). Rinse \u003cstrong\u003echives\u003c/strong\u003e and thinly slice. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73538/recipe_card_size_TlIW8eqhSzaFixaKwFgc_2__Cook_Pasta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eSeason boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003ecavatelli\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring occasionally, until al dente, 11-12 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water \u003c/strong\u003ein a small bowl,\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003ethen drain and set aside (see recipe tip).\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté mushrooms","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73529/recipe_card_size_f0wDhK45TgWiE0jxoaBu_2019-07-03_-_IS_DS_1937_PROCESS3053.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile pasta cooks, heat \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e in a large high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e and sauté, stirring occasionally, until mushrooms begin to brown, 10-12 minutes (this is a great time to set the table). Then, add\u003cstrong\u003e white wine \u003c/strong\u003eand cook, scraping up brown bits from bottom of pan, until liquid is reduced by half, 2-3 minutes more. Season with\u003cstrong\u003e .125 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make porcini broth","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73536/recipe_card_size_EkkVeTLRb24A7igRd4pP_4__Make_Porcini_Broth.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhen cavatelli is cooked and drained, add\u003cstrong\u003e porcini mushroom powder\u003c/strong\u003e to bowl with \u003cstrong\u003ereserved pasta water \u003c/strong\u003eand whisk until fully dissolved.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73535/recipe_card_size_OiQpwxsRRXq470gspYYt_5__Finish_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd cooked \u003cstrong\u003ecavatelli\u003c/strong\u003e to pan with mushrooms, still over medium-high heat, and stir to combine. Add \u003cstrong\u003eporcini broth\u003c/strong\u003e and stir until sauce is silky and clings to pasta, 1-2 minutes. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003emascarpone\u003c/strong\u003e to fully coat pasta, then remove pan from heat. Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate mushroom cavatelli","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/73534/recipe_card_size_QGOnFyaISuWLrddtCscM_6__Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of chives\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e to pan with pasta, still off heat, and stir to combine. Taste and add \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired, then divide \u003cstrong\u003emushroom cavatelli \u003c/strong\u003ebetween serving bowls. Garnish with \u003cstrong\u003eremaining chives \u003c/strong\u003eand\u003cstrong\u003e remaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, and dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"Popular","slug":"customer-favorite","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"Popular","slug":"customer-favorite","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}